25:05.880 --> 25:10.360
So it had to be with somebody who also understood the magic, who knew what the

25:10.360 --> 25:16.440
invocation was to material, not materialize, but to consolidate the spirit and to

25:16.440 --> 25:17.240
get the message.

25:17.600 --> 25:21.120
So it's kind of a complicated procedure, just like with email.

25:21.120 --> 25:27.880
You need machinery at one end to encrypt the message into electrical pulses.

25:27.880 --> 25:32.960
And then you need machinery at the other end to unencrypted, as it were, into a piece

25:32.960 --> 25:35.000
of sensible English.

25:35.680 --> 25:39.320
Dr. Skinner, where have you practiced this?

25:39.360 --> 25:42.040
