35:14.200 --> 35:19.080
One of your primary areas of focus, Dr. Skinner, and it's even in the name of one of your books,

35:19.080 --> 35:23.400
is the techniques, the technological application.

35:23.400 --> 35:29.000
And you mentioned, along with David Rankin in the Goetia of Dr. Rudd, a wonderful tome,

35:29.000 --> 35:37.400
that, quote, the same tables used to encrypt also produced the spirit names, end quote.

35:37.400 --> 35:42.040
So roughly, Dr. Skinner, can you share with listeners who might be hearing about this

35:42.040 --> 35:43.320
for the first time?

35:43.320 --> 35:45.480
How does this whole process work?

35:45.560 --> 35:50.840
Is the practitioner supposed to derive the spirit names first and then encrypt

35:50.840 --> 35:52.280
a message for the spirit?

35:52.280 --> 35:53.400
How does all that work?

